               <p>FOURTEENTH DAY, THURSDAY, SEPTEMBER 24.</p>
               <p>Middlesex Cases, Third Jury. Before W. Arabin, Esq.</p>
               <p>1249. 
               
                  <persName id="t18230910-280-defend2465" type="defendantName">
                     JOSHUA 
                     TAYLOR
